{"tid":674200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估地方] 小六女童遭狼叔性侵懷孕？結果大翻轉　胎兒之父是哥哥","createTime":"2018-05-22T13:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T14:45:25.000Z","uid":78385,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c161f302d5092816cb0ad266846c418f50162758","tid":674200,"uid":78385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T13:12:34.000Z","msg":"女童遭狼叔性侵消息曝光後，父親氣得痛罵弟弟，當場打電話報警抓人，狼叔隨即打包行李連夜逃跑，警方傳喚嫌疑人均未到案，因此遭到通緝。去年被逮後坦承曾性侵姪女，新竹地院依強制性交罪重判8年2月，目前在監服刑當中。<br />\n<br />\n女童進行人工流產後，與狼叔進行DNA比對，結果發現令人意外的事實，胎兒父親並非狼叔，而是親哥哥！女童這才坦言，2015年5月間，哥哥在看完A片後，學片子動作2度對她亂來，但她不希望哥哥被爸媽懲罰，才一直沒有說出口；哥哥也坦承對妹妹下手，新竹檢方昨日依強制性交罪嫌起訴14歲哥哥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://awscdn.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=380610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fawscdn.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D380610&d=lZkW6VhE5WN5Wr719NYtikkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=87fe5618\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fawscdn.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D380610&h=38fe106b\" target=\"_blank\">http://awscdn.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=380610</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新竹連追兩分！"},{"pid":"4c07fe427c6869ef11b86cd29ea75b6451ba72cd","tid":674200,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85618a0bc7452f39f776bff42ffa679ccee06bdf","tid":674200,"uid":79077,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c53a90f2d63a939b30ac3231179e9ff643319882","tid":674200,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"Old news is so exciting"},{"pid":"1ffb44b867a0468d64bd015ee75b4eef8c7831fe","tid":674200,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:16:40.000Z","msg":"肉便器咩戇㞗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dc89cbff048e4f27b45d149b141ede3fc37aa8","tid":674200,"uid":1139